{"type": "article", "id": 26877, "title": "晚霞配色的Stan Smith，以及，H&M 前高管加入 Ralph Lauren｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-16T10:10:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 23146, "name": "杂志封面"}, {"id": 11165, "name": "夏日"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 27657, "name": "定制服务"}, {"id": 7522, "name": "辞职"}, {"id": 13956, "name": "冲浪"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 2911, "name": "Anna Sui"}, {"id": 2840, "name": "Opening Ceremony"}, {"id": 321, "name": "Amazon"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021330063pZunWw6iQC8SbUs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/tiffany-cfo-resignation-human-resources-10429955/\"><b>Tiffany 首席财政官辞职</b></a>｜Tiffany &amp; Co. 首席财政官 Ralph Nicoletti 将于 5 月 20 日离职，已在公司任职两年。而美国 Newell Brands 集团宣布 Ralph Nicoletti 未来将加入公司，6 月 8 日生效，上月 Newell 刚刚收购了 Jarden  集团。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Ralph-Lauren-strengthens-team-with-former-H-M-managers,692785.html\"><b>H&amp;M 前高管加入 Ralph Lauren</b></a>｜去年宣布接替 Ralph Lauren 本人担任 Ralph Lauren CEO 的 Stefan Larsson 曾在 H&amp;M 及 Old Navy 任职多年。自带快消属性的 Larsson 也将任用数名来自 H&amp;M 高管任职各部门的管理人员，从 4 月开始 Fredrik Hjalmers 担任全球扩张及商业开发部门总监，此前他从 2009 年就开始在 H&amp;M 工作。六月，同样来自 H&amp;M 的 Halide Alagöz 将担任全球制造及采购部门总监。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/fendi-peekaboo-karl-lagerfeld-made-to-order-service-in-paris-10429911/\"><b>Fendi 在巴黎提供定制服务</b></a>｜Fendi 1997 年推出的一款以法棍面包命名的包袋 Baguette 一直是多年来最受欢迎的 “It” 包款，而近日 Fendi 又主推 Peekaboo 包，来自 Fendi 罗马工作室的高级设计师上周出现在 Fendi 巴黎旗舰店，为顾客的Peekaboo 包提供定制服务，有一系列皮质及五金配件的选择。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/amazon-apparel-market-10429626/\"><b>2020 年全美服装产业，亚马逊将占据 19%</b></a>｜摩根斯坦利公司（Morgan Stanley）零售团队近日在一份研究报告中表示，预估到 2020 年，亚马逊 （Amazon）的电商品牌将占据全美服装产业的 19%。去年的 179 亿美元，预计占据市场的 6.7%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/5/13/11673692/anna-sui-opening-ceremony-collection#6478833\"><b>Anna Sui 与 Opening Ceremony 推出合作系列</b></a>｜Opening Ceremony 与 Anna Sui 合作，推出一个怀旧系列，几乎复制了 Anna Sui 90 年代最流行的作品，紫色蕾丝吊带、绸缎长裤、丝绒旗袍等等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132949Ng7nyibOf0IBT1Fr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132949QRGSoEBrY2DjaIdU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329501JYk53TuhD2GjLcg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132951vkpx560XPaE49dUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132952hum3V1LE26i7yXxc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132952i7pbQezdPKawCgEk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">夏日临近，Adidas 推出一双晚霞（Sunset Glow）配色 Stan Smith，售价预计在 102 美元。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132953TSGrxsYD65aVBJHp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">冲浪品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/saturdays-nyc-and-mr-porter-summer-collection-2016\">Saturdays NYC 与 MR PORTER 合作推出一个联名系列</a> Smart Summer ，供夏季户外活动及正式场合的几身造型，价格在 65-395 美元之间。<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132953TCkzNsFve3VHKmor.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132954Y72Z6CN0rflJLMtz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132954YvXnKow5V0OWSsP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132954JXtafHlRL92h71DO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329550UNmTisCG3fDhbp1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.786\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132956HFT126L5lReXuQBx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132956TY7PiXAwIVp4qfEQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5503876\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">NikeLab 推出过多款 Air Max 的“升级”或是与其它品牌的合作系列，最新发布的是一个名为  <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/14/nikelab-air-max-pinnacle/#slide-4\">Pinnacle  的全新配色系列</a>，淡白紫和深蓝，系列包含 Air Max 1、the Air Max 90、the Air Max Thea 和 the Pre-Montreal Racer 四款鞋型。<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132957MVPeJ60FxUDs3qAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132957xD72qjsP6FOZyN0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329583pEU86BjnOm5gVJu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132958gVmTzN2hnSsKtDQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132959nT0vJZo7frAKjB52.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132959iIdSBvWLgAT5m8YF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Gap 于 2013 年收购的女装品牌 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/intermix-summer-2016-outfits/\">Intermix 发布夏季 lookbook \"Away She Goes\"</a>，夏季的简约穿搭也不失浪漫：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133000i9Xqr768sJvb52kT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021330006hZwcKozystIi3Ef.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133001YlCA8hgSjdGFuxDZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133001anjsklm9EMJb4wcz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/cos-ifc-new-store/\">COS 在香港 IFC 商场开设全港第四间门店</a>，占地 164 平方米，装修风格延续了一贯的简约美学。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133002GgR7c8wiZPktHUd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133003eC0zwU8slXvPE6N5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133003YkgdEwrvFxKLu4CR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133004H7XS0UaYt5uB43kg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133004pTvO6egiUoLFHMIk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> Kendall Jenner 为最新一期 <i>Harper’s Bazaar </i>拍摄封面、由 Karl Lagerfeld 拍摄。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133004EHbmyBw80M9cJiWF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133005D19bghHL5M2iF3xC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}